**‚ö†Ô∏è Limitations & Best Practices:**

**Storage Limits:**
```javascript
// Typically 5-10MB per domain
console.log('Storage limit reached');

try {
  localStorage.setItem('largeData', hugeString);
} catch (e) {
  if (e.name === 'QuotaExceededError') {
    console.log('Storage is full!');
